*mplayer2-2.0_p20120309 (23 Mar 2012)

  23 Mar 2012; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> +mplayer2-2.0_p20120309.ebuild:
  version bump

  23 Mar 2012; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mplayer2-2.0_p20111126.ebuild,
  mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
  remove obsolete dga and esd USE, update libav dep, disable broken lib

  21 Feb 2012; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mplayer2-2.0_p20111126.ebuild,
  mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
  update linuxtv-dvb-headers category, bug #403929, thanks to Muzer and
  timemanx

  01 Dec 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> -mplayer2-2.0_p20110904.ebuild,
  mplayer2-2.0_p20111126.ebuild, mplayer2-9999.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  sync with portage, remove old

*mplayer2-2.0_p20111126 (28 Nov 2011)

  28 Nov 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> +mplayer2-2.0_p20111126.ebuild:
  new snapshot

  01 Nov 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> -mplayer2-2.0.ebuild,
  -mplayer2-2.0_p20110705.ebuild, -mplayer2-2.0_p20110805.ebuild,
  mplayer2-2.0_p20110904.ebuild, mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
  rename USE v4l2 to v4l while removing support for video4linux 1.x, bug
  #385241

  30 Oct 2011; Nikoli <nikoli@lavabit.com> mplayer2-2.0_p20110904.ebuild,
  mplayer2-9999.ebuild:
  OSD menu was removed upstream, add ~ppc ~ppc64 keywords, better REQUIRED_USE
  usage, fix USE cddb and rsound automagic

